  <entry>
    <title>mit6.s081 环境配置</title>
    <link href="/mit6-s081/mit6.s081-lab-tools/"/>
    <url>/mit6-s081/mit6.s081-lab-tools/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="环境配置"><a href="#环境配置" class="headerlink" title="环境配置"></a>环境配置</h1><p>经过一天的摸索，6.s081的环境终于配置好了，哈哈，分享一下如何配置6.s081的环境。</p><h3 id="本人的硬件、软件"><a href="#本人的硬件、软件" class="headerlink" title="本人的硬件、软件"></a>本人的硬件、软件</h3><p>vmware 16 </p><p>ubuntu 20.04</p><p>2cpu 2cores 8GB ram</p><h3 id="第一步"><a href="#第一步" class="headerlink" title="第一步"></a>第一步</h3><p>需要成功安装ubuntu20.04，这里需要注意一点，网络配置选桥接网络。</p><h3 id="第二步"><a href="#第二步" class="headerlink" title="第二步"></a>第二步</h3><p>换源，将源换成<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/xiangxianghehe/article/details/105688062">中科大源</a></p><p>具体方法是把原先的<code>sources.list</code>的内容全部删掉，之后按照上面链接操作。</p><h3 id="第三步"><a href="#第三步" class="headerlink" title="第三步"></a>第三步</h3><p><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/e90a2b2e8dbd">安装vim</a> </p><h3 id="第四步"><a href="#第四步" class="headerlink" title="第四步"></a>第四步</h3><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/shacheyoumen/article/details/113244366">安装git</a></p><p>直接跑下面代码就行，三行解决</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">sudo apt-get update<br>sudo apt-get upgrade<br>sudo apt-get install git<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>git --version</code>看一下，至少是2.34.1</p><p>之后，将虚拟机的git链接到自己的github</p><h3 id="第五步"><a href="#第五步" class="headerlink" title="第五步"></a>第五步</h3><p><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/yongy1030/p/11699086.html">配置git代理</a></p><h5 id="ip是本机的ip"><a href="#ip是本机的ip" class="headerlink" title="ip是本机的ip"></a><code>ip</code>是本机的<code>ip</code></h5><p>win的话，用<code>ipconfig</code>看，连的无线，用wlan的ipv4地址，有线的话，用以太网的ipv4地址</p><h5 id="port是本机的代理软件的监听本地的端口号"><a href="#port是本机的代理软件的监听本地的端口号" class="headerlink" title="port是本机的代理软件的监听本地的端口号"></a><code>port</code>是本机的代理软件的监听本地的端口号</h5><p>不同软件不同，win的话， 设置 -》网络和Internet -》代理，看监听的是哪个端口号</p><p>代理软件需要开启__允许局域网走流量__</p><h3 id="第六步"><a href="#第六步" class="headerlink" title="第六步"></a>第六步</h3><p><strong>这步开始，我都按照知乎链接跑的</strong>:<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/331492444">知乎</a></p><p>具体如下：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git <span class="hljs-built_in">clone</span> --recursive https://github.com/riscv/riscv-gnu-toolchain<br><br>sudo apt update &amp;&amp; apt upgrade -y<br><br>sudo apt-get install autoconf automake autotools-dev curl libmpc-dev libmpfr-dev libgmp-dev gawk build-essential bison flex texinfo gperf libtool patchutils bc zlib1g-dev libexpat-dev -y<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> riscv-gnu-toolchain<br>./configure --prefix=/usr/<span class="hljs-built_in">local</span><br>sudo make -j4<br><br>sudo apt-get remove qemu-system-misc -y<br>sudo apt-get install qemu-system-misc=1:4.2-3ubuntu6 -y<br><br>git <span class="hljs-built_in">clone</span> git://g.csail.mit.edu/xv6-labs-2020<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> xv6-labs-2020<br>git checkout util<br><br>make qemu<br><br><br>评分系统需要跑python代码<br>sudo ln -s /usr/bin/python3.8 /usr/bin/python<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
